&lt;/h2>&lt;p>In this blog, we have introduced the &lt;strong>basics of wireless hacking&lt;/strong>. We have covered what &lt;strong>WiFi&lt;/strong> is, some important WiFi terms, the history of WiFi, and how WiFi works. In the next blog, we will start covering &lt;strong>wireless attacks&lt;/strong>. &lt;em>Join us for an engaging journey that combines learning, awareness, and securing our wireless connections.&lt;/em>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>